org.yamcs.management

Class ManagementService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.yamcs.management.ManagementService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProcessorListener

    public class ManagementService
extends Object
implements ProcessorListener
    Responsible for providing to interested listeners info related to creation/removal/update of:
    • instances, processors and clients - see ManagementListener
    • links - see LinkListener
    • streams and tables - see TableStreamListener
    • command queues - see CommandQueueListener
